## Icon Library
Always import icons from 'react-coolicons'. Never use @coolicons-dev/solid.

## Icon Name Mapping (Figma → Code)
| Figma Name | Component Name | Package          |
|------------|----------------|------------------|
| info       | Info           | react-coolicons  |

## Correct Usage
import { IconName } from '@coolicons-dev/solid';

// Size using token scale values
<IconName width={16} height={16} color={t.icon.default.subtle} />

## Rules
- Always pass color using icon tokens (t.icon.*.*)
- Never hard-code color values on icons
- Default icon size is 16x16 for inline, 20x20 for standalone

